# Browserslist configuration  
# Target modern browsers only - eliminates ~13KB of legacy polyfills
# Based on Lighthouse report recommendations

# Minimum browser versions (supports all ES2020+ features)
Chrome >= 95
Firefox >= 95
Safari >= 15.4
Edge >= 95

# Mobile browsers
iOS >= 15.4
Android >= 95

# Exclude legacy browsers completely
not dead
not ie 11
not op_mini all
not safari < 15.4
not chrome < 95
not firefox < 95

# This config ensures:
# - No babel transform-classes polyfill needed
# - Native Array.prototype.at/flat/flatMap support
# - Native Object.fromEntries/hasOwn support  
# - Native String trimStart/trimEnd support